Create Select Year Filter Instructions 17

1. Go to any worksheet
2. Drag Class Start Date To Filter.
3. Select Years, click Next then select Use All then click OK



4. Right Click the Filter and select Show Filter.





5. Click the Down Arrow and select Single Value Slider



6. Click the Down Arrow and select Edit Title


7. Erase whatever is in there and replace it with Select Year:

8. Drag the Filter from the Right to the bottom of the Marks Card
